Some tools to run the web frontend for rfc-style rfactor championships and rfactor leagues. 
rFactor is an awsome racing simulator by Image Space Incorporated: http://rfactor.net

reporter.py: checks the rf results directory and POSTs new files to a website

report.php: receives the rfc results files and stashes it to the database

stats.php: displays rfc race statistics

etc.sql: database definitions (mysql)

league_report.php: receives league race results and puts it into the database. also gives points to drivers. integrated with the varjanta (wordpress?) user database

league_stats.php: example frontend for displaying league results 